item.title: Little hope of finding workers alive after tunnel collapse, official says
item.description: An official in India's southern Telangana state says the chances of 8 workers being rescued days after a tunnel collapse are "very, very remote."

item.title: "Security incident" prompts 3-hour lockdown at U.S. Navy base in Italy
item.description: An unspecified "security incident" at U.S. Naval Air Station Sigonella in Italy prompted a shelter-in-place order for several hours.

item.title: Rep. Byron Donalds, backed by Trump, announces run for Florida governor
item.description: Rep. Byron Donalds has announced that he's entering the race to succeed Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis in 2026.

item.title: Man tried to smuggle bags of cocaine under "narco wig," Colombian police say
item.description: Colombian police apprehended a 40-year-old man attempting to smuggle several bags of cocaine concealed beneath a meticulously attached toupee.
